<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL40">
<l>tirumaṟu mārvaniṉṉaic cintaiyuṭ ṭikaḻa vaittu</l>
<l>maruviya maṉatta rākil mānilat tuyirka ḷellām</l>
<l>veruvuṟak koṉṟu cuṭṭiṭ ṭīṭṭiya viṉaiya rēlum</l>
<l>aruviṉaip payaṉa tuyyā raraṅkamā nakaru ḷāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O You with the chest [that bears] Śrī and the mole!</l>
<l>Even if the people who amassed sins by killing [and] burning</l>
<l rend="indent">all the living beings in the world for [them] to be frightened,</l>
<l>if they place You in their minds so that [You] shine [there]</l>
<l rend="indent">and have a manas that meditate [upon You]</l>
<l>they will not experience the fruits of their difficult karman,</l>
<l rend="indent">O You from the big city of Raṅgam!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
